{"tid":2077449,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應蓬佩奧批評　中國外交部：永遠無法叫醒裝睡的人","createTime":"2020-06-24T09:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T10:47:15.000Z","uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"31d84c8b7c62ea7c10e3416936d6544ea726b571","tid":2077449,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"係咪調轉左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅回應美國國務卿蓬佩奧就新疆問題批評中國，認為蓬佩奧近來四處對中國進行莫須有的攻擊，但謊言重複一千遍還是謊言，對方的陳詞濫調，不僅與基本事實嚴重不符，也暴露了他根深蒂固的冷戰零和思維和意識形態偏見，形容「永遠無法叫醒一個裝睡的人」。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅說，中方多次強調，新疆依法設立職業技能教育培訓中心，是為了預防反恐和去極端化而採取的措施，已取得積極成效。新疆連續3年多未發生暴力恐襲案件。截至2019年底，參加培訓的學員已全部結業並實現了穩定就業，過著安寧生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533920-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533920-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPohk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=111e78fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533920-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f8eaa536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533920-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b2e859e2b66c3edce9d25ef1b1702a7034f3a8cc","tid":2077449,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bac74acfae52db41455d5f8a3270d810f73db1","tid":2077449,"uid":247892,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"呢d咪高手<br />\n先發制人<br />\n用哂可以攻擊佢既對白你攻擊你"},{"pid":"c8de8966f76a18d9fc3532b4d0b1e61f541f9d8c","tid":2077449,"uid":28563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06